### 租户级 DataScope 与列表结果集（ITenantDataScopeFilter）
### 说明：创建仅含「查询类」平台权限的角色，数据范围设为 OnlySelf(5)，绑定测试用户后，
###       对用户/资产/审计/项目列表的可见范围应窄于管理员（对比 data.total 或 items 条数）。
### DataScope 枚举：All=0, CurrentTenant=1, CustomDept=2, CurrentDept=3, CurrentDeptAndBelow=4, OnlySelf=5, Project=6
### 若角色 Code 冲突，请修改 @dsRoleCode；若测试用户已存在，请修改 @dsUsername。

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5001
@tenantId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001
@adminUser = admin
@adminPassword = P@ssw0rd!
@dsRoleCode = HTTP_DS_ONLY_SELF
@dsUsername = http_ds_scope_user
@dsPassword = P@ssw0rd!2026
@clientType = WebH5
@clientPlatform = Web
@clientChannel = Browser
@clientAgent = Chrome
@localeZh = zh-CN

### 管理员登录
# @name adminLogin
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/token
Content-Type: application/json
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
X-Client-Type: {{clientType}}
X-Client-Platform: {{clientPlatform}}
X-Client-Channel: {{clientChannel}}
X-Client-Agent: {{clientAgent}}
Accept-Language: {{localeZh}}

{
  "username": "{{adminUser}}",
  "password": "{{adminPassword}}"
}

###
@adminToken = {{adminLogin.response.body.$.data.accessToken}}

### CSRF
# @name antiforgery
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/secure/antiforgery
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
X-Client-Type: {{clientType}}
X-Client-Platform: {{clientPlatform}}
X-Client-Channel: {{clientChannel}}
X-Client-Agent: {{clientAgent}}

###
@csrfToken = {{antiforgery.response.body.$.data.token}}

### 解析 Permission:users:view 的 Id（用于绑定到测试角色）
# @name resolveUsersViewPerm
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/permissions?pageIndex=1&pageSize=5&keyword=Permission:users:view
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

###
@permUsersViewId = {{resolveUsersViewPerm.response.body.$.data.items[0].id}}

### 解析 Permission:assets:view
# @name resolveAssetsViewPerm
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/permissions?pageIndex=1&pageSize=5&keyword=Permission:assets:view
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

###
@permAssetsViewId = {{resolveAssetsViewPerm.response.body.$.data.items[0].id}}

### 解析 Permission:audit:view
# @name resolveAuditViewPerm
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/permissions?pageIndex=1&pageSize=5&keyword=Permission:audit:view
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

###
@permAuditViewId = {{resolveAuditViewPerm.response.body.$.data.items[0].id}}

### 解析 Permission:projects:view
# @name resolveProjectsViewPerm
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/permissions?pageIndex=1&pageSize=5&keyword=Permission:projects:view
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

###
@permProjectsViewId = {{resolveProjectsViewPerm.response.body.$.data.items[0].id}}

### 创建「仅查询 + DataScope」测试角色
# @name createDsRole
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/roles
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
Idempotency-Key: {{$guid}}
X-CSRF-TOKEN: {{csrfToken}}

{
  "name": "HTTP DataScope 测试",
  "code": "{{dsRoleCode}}",
  "description": "仅含列表查询权限，用于 DataScope 验证"
}

###
@dsRoleId = {{createDsRole.response.body.$.data.id}}

### 为测试角色分配查询类权限（不含 users:create 等写权限）
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/roles/{{dsRoleId}}/permissions
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
Idempotency-Key: {{$guid}}
X-CSRF-TOKEN: {{csrfToken}}

{
  "permissionIds": [{{permUsersViewId}}, {{permAssetsViewId}}, {{permAuditViewId}}, {{permProjectsViewId}}]
}

### 设置角色数据范围为「仅本人」OnlySelf = 5
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/roles/{{dsRoleId}}/data-scope
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
Idempotency-Key: {{$guid}}
X-CSRF-TOKEN: {{csrfToken}}

{
  "dataScope": 5,
  "deptIds": []
}

### 创建测试用户并绑定上述角色
# @name createDsUser
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
Idempotency-Key: {{$guid}}
X-CSRF-TOKEN: {{csrfToken}}

{
  "username": "{{dsUsername}}",
  "password": "{{dsPassword}}",
  "displayName": "HTTP DataScope 用户",
  "email": "http.ds.scope@atlas.local",
  "phoneNumber": "13800000002",
  "isActive": true,
  "roleIds": [{{dsRoleId}}],
  "departmentIds": [],
  "positionIds": []
}

###
@dsUserId = {{createDsUser.response.body.$.data.id}}

### [基线] 管理员 — 用户列表（通常为租户全量或策略内全量）
# @name adminUsersPage
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users?pageIndex=1&pageSize=50
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### [基线] 管理员 — 资产列表
# @name adminAssetsPage
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/assets?pageIndex=1&pageSize=50
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### [基线] 管理员 — 审计列表
# @name adminAuditPage
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/audit?pageIndex=1&pageSize=50
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### [基线] 管理员 — 项目列表
# @name adminProjectsPage
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/projects?pageIndex=1&pageSize=50
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### DataScope 用户登录
# @name dsUserLogin
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/token
Content-Type: application/json
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
X-Client-Type: {{clientType}}
X-Client-Platform: {{clientPlatform}}
X-Client-Channel: {{clientChannel}}
X-Client-Agent: {{clientAgent}}

{
  "username": "{{dsUsername}}",
  "password": "{{dsPassword}}"
}

###
@dsToken = {{dsUserLogin.response.body.$.data.accessToken}}

### [DataScope] 受限用户 — 用户列表（预期 total 显著小于管理员基线，多数场景仅本人）
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users?pageIndex=1&pageSize=50
Authorization: Bearer {{dsToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### [DataScope] 受限用户 — 资产列表
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/assets?pageIndex=1&pageSize=50
Authorization: Bearer {{dsToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### [DataScope] 受限用户 — 审计列表
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/audit?pageIndex=1&pageSize=50
Authorization: Bearer {{dsToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### [DataScope] 受限用户 — 项目列表
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/projects?pageIndex=1&pageSize=50
Authorization: Bearer {{dsToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### [反向 401] 未认证 — 用户列表
# @expected-status 401
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users?pageIndex=1&pageSize=10
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
